Prerequisite:
Libdrm

Note:
Module "stm" is hard coded. Please change accoring to your board

Compile program on target:
gcc drm_multitouch.c -o drm_multitouch -I/usr/include/drm/ -ldrm -lm -lpthread

Cross Compile:
<cross-compiler-prefix>-gcc drm_multitouch.c -o drm_multitouch -I<libdrm_inc_path> -I<libdrm_inc_path>/drm -L<libdrm_lib_path> -ldrm -lm -lpthread
